code: export const handleCheckAnswers=async(data,setSessionData)=>{try{const response=await fetch("http://localhost:8000/check-answers",{credentials:"include"});if(response.ok){const data=await response.json();if(data){setSessionData(data.sessionData);}}else{console.error("Failed to retrieve session data.");}}catch(error){console.error("Error retrieving session data:",error);}};
